00:22:21.146 --> 00:22:22.238
Rupa!

00:22:24.145 --> 00:22:25.672
Thakuma...

00:22:32.374 --> 00:22:33.861
Apakah dia duduk dengan tenang di dalam?

00:22:34.020 --> 00:22:35.631
